{"tid":137912,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"薩爾瓦多動物園河馬遭虐打致死","createTime":"2017-02-28T07:48:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T07:48:24.000Z","uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"67b62284154c0beab473b22de78939dce182c4b1","tid":137912,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T07:48:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=212324&amp;refer=share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212324%26refer%3Dshare&d=2WRE5dcwgWUU%2Ft06b4Zyy%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=ad79e5c1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D212324%26refer%3Dshare&h=49f66d92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=212324&amp;refer=share</a><br />\n<br />\nNow新聞台】身形肥胖的河馬看似溫馴，實則極為兇猛，一旦發惡，鱷魚也能咬死。鱷魚也不怕的河馬卻敵不過人類，被人類虐打至死。<br />\n美聯社報道，中美洲國家薩爾瓦多一間動物園所飼養的河馬古斯塔維托，於上周二晚被虐打至遍體鱗傷，事後牠一直躲在園內的水池中不出來，飼養員延至周四才發現牠的傷勢，園方隨即派人搶救，但牠最終於周日不治。<br />\n當局事後檢驗河馬的屍體，發現牠身上多處瘀傷及刺傷，相信曾被人用鐵棒、刀及石頭虐打，暫時未知肇事者身分及動機。"}]}